<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <h1><%= course.title %> - <%= title %></h1>
  <p><a href="/courses/<%= course.id %>">강의 상세로 돌아가기</a></p>

  <h2>출석 현황</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>총 결석 횟수: <%= absentCount %>회</li>
    <li>총 지각 횟수: <%= lateCount %>회</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>점수 계산</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>총 감점: <%= totalPenalty %>점</li>
    <li><strong>최종 출석 점수: <%= finalScore %> / <%= maxScore %>점</strong></li>
  </ul>

</body>
</html>
